data.description:
This lovely home has been tastefully updated throughout. This spacious 1,184 sq.ft. home offers a bright and open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a large garage.  With an updated kitchen, new contemporary laminate flooring throughout, fresh interior paint, and set back on a privately gated property, it’s the perfect place to call home. 
You will be delighted as you walk in the front door to the charming family room with two large windows allowing lots of natural light to filter in, craftsman crown molding and baseboards, and trendy wide plank richly colored  laminate flooring. This space flows nicely into the large eat-in kitchen complete with modern granite counter tops, stylish mohagany finished cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a picturesque corner window. It’s the perfect place to gather with friends and family.  
The extended hallway leads to a stunning and completely updated full bath!  New flooring, sleek custom surround shower tile, new vanity with modern solid counter top, and contemporary finished fixtures. The bathroom is flanked by a large alcove and two roomy bedrooms with more impressive bay windows giving them a bright and airy feel.  Tucked in the back of the long hallway the master suite awaits. It’s an intimate and grand haven with beautiful windows, a private full bathroom that includes a solid vanity counter top and shower surround, an ample sized closet, and more craftsman finishing touches throughout.  It’s the perfect place to retreat, relax, and rejuvinate. 
Centrally located in Richmond, this adorable home provides easy access to the Richmond Parkway, I-80, and 580 Freeways. It’s conveniently situated close to the Hilltop District which provides restaurants, mall shopping and a theater. It’s also in close proximity to the Shields-Ried Community Center, a local neighborhood favorite, and the Wildcat Marsh S.F. trail head for the hiking, mountain biking, and nature enthusiasts. It offers the best of East Bay living in a charming family friendly neighborhood.
